original_title: Queens: Lincoln Street - Van Wyck Boulevard
text:
Lincoln Street, south side, east of Van Wyck Boulevard, showing the Greenwood house, which has been in the Van Sicklen family from some date prior to 1859.

1922.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
